	PR modula2/109103
	* gm2-compiler/M2ALU.def (PushString): New parameter issueError.
	* gm2-compiler/M2ALU.mod (PushString): New parameter issueError.
	* gm2-compiler/SymbolTable.mod (PushString): New parameter issueError.
